value-key.description: Enter the name of the key to be displayed in the suggested object
value-key.description_zh: 输入建议对象中用于显示的键名

value.description: Required value, enter the binding value

:debounce.description: Get the input suggested debounce delay
:debounce.description_zh: 获取输入建议的去抖延时

:fetch-suggestions.description: Returns an input suggestion method, only when your input suggests data Resolve, by calling callback(data:[]).
:fetch-suggestions.description_zh: 返回输入建议的方法，仅当你的输入建议数据 resolve 时，通过调用 callback(data:[]) 来返回它

popper-class.description: The class name of the Autocomplete drop-down list

trigger-on-focus.description: Whether to display a list of suggestions when the input box is focused
trigger-on-focus.description_zh: 是否在输入框 focus 时显示建议列表

select-when-unmatched.description: In the absence of any matching suggestions, press enter to trigger the select event
select-when-unmatched.description_zh: 在输入没有任何匹配建议的情况下，按下回车是否触发 select 事件

label.description: Enter the label text associated with the field

hide-loading.description: Whether to hide the loading icon when loading remotely
hide-loading.description_zh: 是否隐藏远程加载时的加载图标

popper-append-to-body.description: Whether to insert a drop-down list into the body element. If there is a problem with the positioning of the drop-down list, you can set the property to false
popper-append-to-body.description_zh: 是否将下拉列表插入至 body 元素。在下拉列表的定位出现问题时，可将该属性设置为 false

highlight-first-item.description: Whether the first item in the remote search suggestion is highlighted by default
highlight-first-item.description_zh: 是否默认突出显示远程搜索建议中的第一项

events.name: select
events.description: Triggered when you click to select a suggestion
events.description_zh: 点击选中建议项时触发

events.name: change
events.description: Triggers when the Input value changes
events.description_zh: 在 Input 值改变时触发

slots.name: prefix
slots.description: Enter the content of the header of the box

slots.name: suffix
slots.description: Enter the content at the end of the box

slots.name: prepend
slots.description: The input box is preceded by content

slots.name: append
slots.description: The input box is followed by the content
